      "new_content_preview": "\n--=======================================================================\n-- *** [PRICE BREAKDOWN - INSERTED SECTION] ***\n-- SOURCE  : #Step3Bundle (post-LEAD slot computation, post-NCCI bundling)\n--           joined to #Step4 for encounter-level suppression decisions.\n--\n-- #Step3Bundle is built as SELECT s.*, CAST(0 AS TINYINT) AS NeedsCorrectedClaim\n-- INTO #Step3Bundle FROM #Step3 s \u2014 all #Step3 columns survive plus NeedsCorrectedClaim.\n-- #Step3 carries an explicit column list that includes all LEAD slot columns\n-- (RD1-RD10, RDC1-RDC10, Therapy1-Therapy10) and all pricing category colum",
